  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Prepare the falafel according to the package instructions and bake for 20 minutes.",
    "In a pan, saute the sliced bitter melon with a little oil until it is tender.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the cooked vermicelli noodles, grated carrots, sliced cucumber, and pickled ginger.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the sriracha sauce and rice vinegar.",
    "Add the cooked falafel, sauteed bitter melon, and marinated tofu to the bowl with the noodles and vegetables.",
    "Pour the sriracha sauce mixture over the top and toss to combine.",
    "Garnish with chopped mint leaves and serve immediately."
